1.0.0.name: wordpress/taxcaster
1.0.0.description:
This plugin embeds the TaxCaster Lite Tax Refund Estimator application on any post or page in WordPress

Estimate your 2011 tax refund. How big will your tax refund be? This application makes it easy to find out how much you’re going to get back from Uncle Sam this year or how much you’ll owe.

View the full TaxCaster Calculator
